snippet.title: Rugrats: Adventures in Gameland DEMO TRAILER LIVE on STEAM
snippet.description:
Rugrats: Adventures in Gameland DEMO LIVE NOW ON STEAM

Tommy, Chucky, Lily, and Phil are off to their most fantastic adventure yet. The baby's reality meets imagination in a new NES game made from scratch in 2024, with the technology to switch from 8-bit to HD hand-drawn art within seconds. 

Play the demo now on Steam and it to your wishlist.
https://tinyurl.com/RugratsSteamDemo

Available this Spring/Summer on Xbox/S/X, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, Steam PC

Pre-order the game today through Limited Run Games:
https://limitedrungames.com/collections/rugrats-adventures-in-gameland
